

============================================================================

CODEOWNERS — Cipher-tube

============================================================================



This file defines code-ownership rules that drive automatic PR review

assignment. Ownership aligns with the pillar-based governance model

documented in CONTRIBUTING.md.



Rules are evaluated bottom-to-top — later patterns take precedence.

Teams must be created under the GitHub organization before this file

takes effect. Replace @cipher-tube/ prefixes with your org handle.

============================================================================


